Dorothy Stone (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Stone_(actress) 0 Dorothy Stone (June 3, 1905 – September 24, 1974) (a/k/a Dorothy B. Stone and Dorothy Stone Collins) was an actress, dancer, and singer in theater and motion pictures, born in Brooklyn, New York.
